channel.title: 562 Trade Bug
channel.description: I have this trade bug that when a player trades 29+ of a noted item, the other player wouldn't receive the item. And if the player has no inventory space left for what the other guy has to trade, the trade will still accept, it wont say "The other player doesn't have enough inventory space". Its not my trade.java or container.java because I already tried replacing it with other sources. Any help?
